</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F90ECF21EC51FF9EB1E3F82FFE2EF83C" blockId="2.[151,1437,1667,2017]" pageId="2" pageNumber="69">
<emphasis id="CBC51333EC51FF9EB1E3F82FFE9EF860" box="[199,260,1955,1981]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="69">Head</emphasis>
and labial palpus pale brown; antenna brown, weakly serrate and somewhat flattened in male, filiform in female; proboscis absent.
</paragraph>
