</emphasis>
: 
<emphasis id="CBC51333EC57FF98B28FFAD5FC50FAAC" bold="true" box="[939,970,1369,1393]" pageId="4" pageNumber="71">10.</emphasis>
Biotope near a subtropical mixed forest; 
<emphasis id="CBC51333EC57FF98B45AFAD5FA06FAAC" bold="true" box="[1406,1436,1369,1393]" pageId="4" pageNumber="71">11.</emphasis>
